::KitKat::

She runs after them, following thier scent trail.  She knows that 
heading for the maximal base was suicided.  But those two had no idea 
what they were up against.  She ran as fast as her legs could carry 
her.  She opened up her commlink, "Land Mine, Time Bomb, return to 
base now or you will deal with me, understood. Get back here now!"
she kept running hoping to catch them in time.
